title: Quadro Set of 6 Spirit Tumblers
features: Stylish contemporary spirit tumbler for whisky
Square base with unique twisted profile
Handmade by Bohemia Crystal and supplied in blue a Bohemia Glassware box
description: This is a thoroughly modern crystalline spirit tumbler set, made by the world famous glass factory of Bohemia Crystal. The tumbler is square at the base and round at the rim, the four sides having a distinctive twist which provides Quadro with its unique contemporary design. Made from crystalline, the Quadro tumbler has a comfortable balanced feel in the hand. This set of 6 tumblers are a perfect compliment to the Quadro decanter range. If you are looking to replace your tired old tumblers then the Quadro Tumbler Set is a good choice and an ideal gift for Christmas, birthday or retirement.
